<! [CDATA[
 Daelim Industrial Logo
Daelim Industrial was established in 1939, and its E&C and Petrochemical Groups are the main lead of the Daelim Business Conglomerate. The fields covered by Daelim Industrial as one of the top EPC Company in Asia to the Middle East include gas, petroleum refining, chemical and petrochemical, power and energy plants, building and housing, civil works, and industrial facilities. Daelim Group is considered one of the top and largest chaebol companies in South Korea.
You can download theDaelimlogo on full-version of the page.
